message.text:
🚨 Audition Update! 🚨

Heads up, Chorale fam! 🎶 Unfortunately, today’s auditions are postponed due to unexpected circumstances. We truly appreciate your patience and understanding, and we’ll be announcing the updated schedule very soon. 💚

But here’s some good news — auditions scheduled for tomorrow, September 16, will still push through as planned! 🌟 So if you’ve been preparing your pieces, don’t worry, you’ll still get the chance to showcase your talent and be part of the FEU Chorale family. 💛✨

Thank you for bearing with us as we make these adjustments. We’re excited to hear your voices, and we’ll keep you posted on the new date for today’s postponed session. Stay tuned here on our page for updates! 💫

#FEUChorale #FEU #Auditions #FEUChoraleAuditions #KanTamaraw #TamarawTalent

message.text:
🚨 Audition Update! 🚨

Heads up, Chorale fam! 🎶 Unfortunately, today’s auditions are postponed due to unexpected circumstances. We truly appreciate your patience and understanding, and we’ll be announcing the updated schedule very soon. 💚

But here’s some good news — auditions scheduled for tomorrow, September 16, will still push through as planned! 🌟 So if you’ve been preparing your pieces, don’t worry, you’ll still get the chance to showcase your talent and be part of the FEU Chorale family. 💛✨

Thank you for bearing with us as we make these adjustments. We’re excited to hear your voices, and we’ll keep you posted on the new date for today’s postponed session. Stay tuned here on our page for updates! 💫

#FEUChorale #FEU #Auditions #FEUChoraleAuditions #KanTamaraw #TamarawTalent

message.text:
🚨 Audition Update! 🚨

Heads up, Chorale fam! 🎶 Unfortunately, today’s auditions are postponed due to unexpected circumstances. We truly appreciate your patience and understanding, and we’ll be announcing the updated schedule very soon. 💚

But here’s some good news — auditions scheduled for tomorrow, September 16, will still push through as planned! 🌟 So if you’ve been preparing your pieces, don’t worry, you’ll still get the chance to showcase your talent and be part of the FEU Chorale family. 💛✨

Thank you for bearing with us as we make these adjustments. We’re excited to hear your voices, and we’ll keep you posted on the new date for today’s postponed session. Stay tuned here on our page for updates! 💫

#FEUChorale #FEU #Auditions #FEUChoraleAuditions #KanTamaraw #TamarawTalent
